OL,3,CFormer union leader told Post Office
OL,4,Cabout subpostmasters 'sniffing around'
OL,6,FThe former head of the union for
OL,7,Fsubpostmasters privately tipped off
OL,8,Fthe Post Office about those "sniffing
OL,9,Faround" the Horizon IT system, an
OL,10,Finquiry heard.
OL,12,FGeorge Thomson, former general
OL,13,Fsecretary of the National Federation
OL,14,Fof Subpostmasters (NFSP), also
OL,15,Fappeared to admit he knew the Post
OL,16,FOffice helpline was telling
OL,17,Fsubpostmasters to make up shortfalls
OL,18,Fin their accounts themselves.
