OL,3,CFormer union leader told Post Office
OL,4,Cabout subpostmasters 'sniffing around'
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the Trades Union
OL,7,FCongress said the Communication
OL,8,FWorkers Union (CWU) was blocked from
OL,9,Feffectively organising at the Post
OL,10,FOffice, claiming the NFSP was given
OL,11,Ffunds by the Post Office.
OL,13,FMr Thomson, who served as general
OL,14,Fsecretary between 2007 and 2018, gave
OL,15,Fevidence at the Post Office inquiry on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FThe inquiry was shown an email from
OL,19,FMark Davies, communications and
OL,20,Fcorporate affairs director at the Post
OL,21,FOffice, sent on May 10 2015.
