OL,3,CFormer union leader told Post Office
OL,4,Cabout subpostmasters 'sniffing around'
OL,6,FPart of the email read: "Our media
OL,7,Frelationships with George (Thomson)
OL,8,Fand team are very good at present ` he
OL,9,Fhas been tipping us off, privately,
OL,10,Fabout people sniffing around Horizon."
OL,12,FAsked by inquiry counsel Julian Blake
OL,13,Fif that was the case, Mr Thomson said
OL,14,FHorizon was a "robust" system and that
OL,15,Fhe worked closely with the Post Office
OL,16,Fto strengthen the franchise.
OL,18,FMr Thomson added: "The better you can
OL,19,Fmake a franchise, the more better
OL,20,Frewarded your members will be."
