OL,6,FThe inquiry was also shown an open
OL,7,Fletter from union member Chris Neill
OL,8,Fto the NFSP's executive committee from
OL,9,FJuly 2013, which stated fellow members
OL,10,Ffelt "abandoned by our general
OL,11,Fsecretary" and that he could "almost
OL,12,Fbe accused of complicity with the Post
OL,13,FOffice".
OL,15,FAsked by Mr Blake why he did not see
OL,16,F"looking out for the little guy" as
OL,17,Fpart of your job, Mr Thomson said: "I
OL,18,Fwas careful not to be seen to be
OL,19,Fcrying wolf."
