OL,6,FMr Thomson told the inquiry there were
OL,7,Fdiscussions in 2013 around the NFSP's
OL,8,Flong-term future and whether it had
OL,9,Fenough resources to continue.
OL,11,FPut to him by Mr Blake that it was
OL,12,Fimportant to keep the Post Office on
OL,13,Fside so they could provide future
OL,14,Ffunding, Mr Thomson said: "I disagree
OL,15,Fwith that.
OL,17,F"We did not change our view on Horizon
OL,18,Fbecause we were looking at our future
OL,19,Fand where we were going to go,
OL,20,Fabsolutely not."
