OL,6,FThe inquiry had earlier been shown an
OL,7,Femail sent on behalf of Mr Thomson in
OL,8,FAugust 2013, which outlined plans for
OL,9,Fthe Post Office and NFSP to sign a 15-
OL,10,Fyear contract to represent all post
OL,11,Foffice operators.
OL,13,FThis included annual payments starting
OL,14,Fat #500,000 in 2013-14 and reaching
OL,15,F#2.5 million from 2017 onwards to 2028.
