OL,3,CFormer union leader told Post Office
OL,4,Cabout subpostmasters 'sniffing around'
OL,6,FPut to him that the NFSP was
OL,7,Ffinancially dependent on the Post
OL,8,FOffice at a time when issues with
OL,9,FHorizon were ongoing, Mr Thomson said
OL,10,Fthe money was "replacing what used to
OL,11,Fbe membership money" after losing
OL,12,F8,500 subpostmasters, adding: "It was
OL,13,Fnever ever tied to Horizon."
OL,15,FThe inquiry was shown a Computer
OL,16,FWeekly article from May 2009 which
OL,17,Fdiscussed the cases of several high-
OL,18,Fprofile subpostmasters, including Sir
OL,19,FAlan Bates.
