OL,3,CFormer union leader told Post Office
OL,4,Cabout subpostmasters 'sniffing around'
OL,6,FThe subpostmasters told the media
OL,7,Foutlet their union had "refused to
OL,8,Fhelp them investigate their concerns".
OL,10,FAsked by Mr Blake why the NFSP was not
OL,11,Fhelping them, Mr Thomson said the
OL,12,Ffederation had to seek permission from
OL,13,Fthe Post Office first.
OL,15,FHe said: "Every case that was brought
OL,16,Fto us, we took it up with the Post
OL,17,FOffice.
OL,19,F"You're trying to make out that
OL,20,Fsomehow we were flush with money...
OL,21,FThat's not correct."
