OL,3,CFormer union leader told Post Office
OL,4,Cabout subpostmasters 'sniffing around'
OL,6,FMr Thomson said he had investigated 20
OL,7,For 30 subpostmaster cases at the
OL,8,F"highest level" during his time as
OL,9,Fgeneral secretary and would have tried
OL,10,Fto employ a computer expert had he
OL,11,Fknown more about the issues with
OL,12,FHorizon.
OL,14,FOn the Horizon IT system, Mr Thomson
OL,15,Fsaid: "It's a strong system, it's a
OL,16,Fwell-used system, and I still support
OL,17,Fit systemically as being very robust."
