OL,4,Cabout subpostmasters 'sniffing around'
OL,6,FHe also criticised all television
OL,7,Fprogrammes made about the Horizon IT
OL,8,Fscandal, such as a BBC Panorama
OL,9,Finvestigation, as he said they
OL,10,F"haven't given a balance".
OL,12,FMore than 700 subpostmasters were
OL,13,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,14,F1999 and 2015 when errors in the Post
OL,15,FOffice's Horizon IT system meant money
OL,16,Fappeared to be missing from many
OL,17,Fbranch accounts when, in fact, it was
OL,18,Fnot.
